{"tid":1933322,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普擬提名上將級衛生部長加入世衛執行委員會 以進一步參與世衛運作","createTime":"2020-03-19T08:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T08:36:42.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ab157c4fc6dcdf2336f26cd86a7aa428c9d1a6f5","tid":1933322,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/03/19/php9MXKDZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F03%2F19%2Fphp9MXKDZ.jpg&h=1a145ab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國政府將提名衛生部助理部長吉羅伊爾（見圖）為WHO執委會代表。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n2020-03-19 06:51:13<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，下稱武漢肺炎）疫情在美國迅速擴散，美國政府及國會實施一系列緊急應變政策與經濟紓困方案。除了對內措施，美國總統川普也有意進一步參與世界衛生組織（WHO）運作，將派代表進入WHO執行委員會。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導，川普將提名美國公共衛生服務軍官團上將、衛生部助理部長吉羅伊爾（Brett Giroir）為WHO執委會美國代表，此提名案須經過參議院同意。WHO執委會由34名全球公衛專家組成，但美國的席位直到目前仍從缺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3104825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3104825&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFaEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=be3f9efc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3104825&h=ab264fdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3104825</a>"},{"pid":"650f8fde9cc237a5075385375abb7a93db01bc83","tid":1933322,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:36:42.000Z","msg":"入去要攞主導權查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}